source:
TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_SEQ_00<tab>The course chaperone would invite you to prove your skills in a timeless test of acrobatic aptitude.
※This quest is available for a limited time only.
target:
TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_SEQ_00<tab>* <var 1A 02 /var>Cette quête est un événement à durée limitée.<var 1A 01 /var>

Le responsable des ins<var 16 /var>crip<var 16 /var>tions de “Pas dans l'tas” vous regarde avec des yeux brillants.

source: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_SEQ_01<tab>Perhaps against your better judgment, you have elected to take on the Eorzean Nimble Warrior obstacle course, which has been revamped this year to be more challenging than ever. As per Beaudefoin's instructions, propel yourself up to the starting line by hopping on the nearby water spout, then carefully make your way across a series of precarious platforms to reach the midway point. When you arrive, be sure to report to the chaperone stationed there before proceeding on to the finish.
target:
TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_SEQ_01<tab>Cette quête ne peut être commencée et effectuée que pendant la durée de l'événement saisonnier correspondant. Pour plus de détails, veuillez consulter The Lodestone.

La responsable des ins<var 16 /var>crip<var 16 /var>tions de l'attraction “Pas dans l'tas” s'est occupé d'enregistrer votre par<var 16 /var>ti<var 16 /var>ci<var 16 /var>pa<var 16 /var>tion et Beaudefoin vous a expliqué comment procéder<var 1D /var>: utiliser le petit geyser pour monter, atteindre la mi-parcours et s'adresser à la personne là-bas, puis se diriger vers l'arrivée où attend P'obyano. Commencez par aller parler au responsable de mi-parcours.

source: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_SEQ_02<tab>Though there were times when you thought you might take an unfortunate tumble, you have impressively managed to reach the midway point of the Eorzean Nimble Warrior course. The chaperone in attendance offers you words of congratulations and caution before encouraging you to forge your way forward to the finish line, where her colleague P'obyano awaits.
target: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_SEQ_02<tab>Celui-ci vous a félicité<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> et vous a encouragé<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> à poursuivre vos efforts jusqu'à l'arrivée où vous attend P'obyano.

source: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_SEQ_03<tab>You have successfully navigated your way to the finish line of the Eorzean Nimble Warrior course, doubtless to the joy of anyone who was fortunate enough to witness your remarkable run. You claim your hard-earned prize of four Faire vouchers, leaving open the option of returning to showcase your skills yet again while the festivities are still ongoing.
target: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_SEQ_03<tab>La Miqo'te du comité d'or<var 16 /var>ga<var 16 /var>ni<var 16 /var>sa<var 16 /var>tion des Feux de la Mort vous a congratulé<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> pour votre performance et vous a invité<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> à participer à nouveau à cette attraction.
TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_TODO_00<tab>Faire un rapport au responsable de mi-parcours

source: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_STAFF03665_100_000<tab>Welcome, friend. I trust you're here to try your hand─or would that be your feet?─at the Eorzean Nimble Warrior course, yes? Wonderful! My colleague here will get you signed up straightaway!
target: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_STAFF03665_100_000<tab>Bienvenue à “Pas dans l'tas”<var 1D /var>! L'attraction phare des Feux de la Mort<var 1D /var>! Vous voulez participer<var 1D /var>? Je m'en occupe<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_BEAUDEFOIN_000_000<tab>Well, now <var 1A 02 /var>there's<var 1A 01 /var> a face I'd recognize anywhere! Welcome back, friend, and many thanks for joining us at this year's festivities! I trust you're ready to amaze onlookers with your characteristic brand of athletic derring-do?
target: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_BEAUDEFOIN_000_000<tab>Hé, saluuut<var 1D /var>! Ça fait un bail, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var><var 1D /var>! Je savais bien que tu viendrais<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_BEAUDEFOIN_000_001<tab>Welcome, my friend, and many thanks for joining us at this year's festivities! I trust you're ready to amaze onlookers with your characteristic brand of athletic derring-do?
target: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_BEAUDEFOIN_000_001<tab>Hé, saluuut<var 1D /var>! J'étais impatient de voir arriver un nouveau participant<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_BEAUDEFOIN_000_002<tab>Very well, then! Without further ado, allow me to explain the rules of the challenge in full. Pay close attention, now─you never know what small morsel of knowledge may prove the difference between a glorious victory and a humiliating defeat!
target: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_BEAUDEFOIN_000_002<tab>Je vais d'abord t'expliquer les règles, alors ouvre grand tes oreilles<var 1D /var>! Pour commencer, tu dois monter sur le petit geyser un peu plus loin pour arriver tout en haut du parcours de “Pas dans l'tas”<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_BEAUDEFOIN_000_003<tab>First, just hop atop that jet of water and let it propel you with a splash to the start of the course! From there, you'll have to navigate a sequence of precarious platforms and narrow ledges to make your way to the central checkpoint. Two hints for you: move cautiously, and try not to look down!
target: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_BEAUDEFOIN_000_003<tab>Une fois là-haut, tu devras te diriger vers le responsable de mi-parcours<var 1D /var>! Mais fais bien attention à ne pas tomber en route<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_BEAUDEFOIN_000_004<tab>When you reach the checkpoint, the first thing you'll want to do is speak with the chaperone stationed there. It's her job to confirm that all competitors have completed the full course fair and square, you see. From there, it's a straight shot to the goal, where my colleague P'obyano awaits.
target: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_BEAUDEFOIN_000_004<tab>Une fois que tu auras passé cette étape, il ne te restera plus qu'à viser l'arrivée<var 1D /var>! Ma collègue P'obyano t'y accueillera<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_BEAUDEFOIN_000_005<tab>The course may appear imposing, as well it should─Master Gegeruju's really pulled out all the stops this year. But fear not! You can take as much time as you'd like, and in the event that you should take an unfortunate and premature tumble, you can simply swim your way back to the starting point and try again!
target: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_BEAUDEFOIN_000_005<tab>Ne t'inquiète pas<var 1D /var>! Il n'y a aucune contrainte de temps, ni même de pénalité si tu tombes<var 1D /var>! Dans l'éventualité où tu glisserais, tu n'auras qu'à utiliser un petit geyser pour remonter et poursuivre ta course<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_BEAUDEFOIN_000_006<tab>Are you ready? Then have at it! My colleagues and I will be cheering you on from down below!
target: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_BEAUDEFOIN_000_006<tab>Alors, prêt<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> à te lancer<var 1D /var>? Vas-y, fais-moi un grand saut et bon courage<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_BEAUDEFOIN_000_007<tab>Welcome back, my athletically accomplished friend! Back to amaze onlookers with another remarkable run at the Eorzean Nimble Warrior course, are we? Splendid! You already know the rules, so feel free to hop right onto that water spout and show everyone what you've got!
target: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_BEAUDEFOIN_000_007<tab>Héhé, saluuut<var 1D /var>! Je savais que tu reviendrais participer à “Pas dans l'tas”<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_BEAUDEFOIN_000_008<tab>Oh, and don't forget to report to the chaperone at the checkpoint, yes? We wouldn't want all to see all your efforts go for naught, now would we? But enough of my ramblings. Go forth, brave and honorable Nimble Warror!
target: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_BEAUDEFOIN_000_008<tab>Tu n'as pas oublié<var 1D /var>? Il faut d'abord que tu montes grâce au petit geyser<var 1D /var>! Surtout, pense à t'adresser au responsable de mi-parcours<var 1D /var>! Vas-y, c'est quand tu veux<var 1D /var>! Bon courage<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_BEAUDEFOIN_000_009<tab>Your first objective is to make it to the checkpoint midway through. Remember to speak with the chaperone there before forging on to the finish line, or your triumph won't count and your acrobatic exploits will all have been in vain!
target: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_BEAUDEFOIN_000_009<tab>Tu dois d'abord atteindre la mi-parcours<var 1D /var>! N'oublie pas de t'adresser au responsable qui est là-bas, surtout<var 1D /var>! Amuse-toi bien<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_BEAUDEFOIN_000_010<tab>Most impressive, my swift and sprightly friend! I was convinced you were going to make it clear to the finish line in one fell swoop! You may have fallen short, but sweet victory is right there for the taking! Now get back out there and show the adoring crowds what you've got!
target: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_BEAUDEFOIN_000_010<tab>Ouah<var 1D /var>! Je suis vraiment im<var 16 /var>pres<var 16 /var>sion<var 16 /var>né<var 1D /var>! Continue comme ça, surtout<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_STAFF03665_100_011<tab>The course will give you a challenge, but it's far from impossible─especially for an experienced adventurer like yourself, I'd wager! Keep your eyes on your landing point, don't rush your jumps, and most importantly...try not to look down!
target: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_STAFF03665_100_011<tab>Le meilleur moyen de réussir à “Pas dans l'tas”, c'est de bien regarder l'endroit où l'on va atterrir et de sauter sans s'affoler<var 1D /var>! Je vous souhaite bon courage<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_FESSUMSTAFF03665_000_020<tab>Congratulations! You've made it to the halfway point! And as challenging as this course is, I daresay that's an accomplishment in itself.
target: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_FESSUMSTAFF03665_000_020<tab>Bravo<var 1D /var>! Vous avez atteint la mi-parcours<var 1D /var>! Je valide votre passage<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_FESSUMSTAFF03665_000_021<tab>So pat yourself on the back and feel free to take a breather before you venture on. My colleague P'obyano is waiting at the finish line. Can you make your way there and claim your reward? I guess we'll see, won't we!
target: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_FESSUMSTAFF03665_000_021<tab>Continuez comme ça<var 1D /var>! L'arrivée n'est plus très loin<var 1D /var>! Lorsque vous y serez, adressez-vous à P'obyano<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_FESSUMSTAFF03665_000_022<tab>Feel proud, friend! Why, many of your ungainly peers never even make it this far. But don't get too comfortable yet! Half of the course still remains, and the road won't be an easy one.
target: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_FESSUMSTAFF03665_000_022<tab>Continuez comme ça<var 1D /var>! L'arrivée n'est plus très loin<var 1D /var>! Lorsque vous y serez, adressez-vous à P'obyano<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_POBYANO_000_030<tab>You did it! And just as I thought you would! Right from the start, when I saw you leaping and bounding your way through the course like it was nothing, I had a feeling you were a Moonfire Faire veteran. And now I see that I was right!
target: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_POBYANO_000_030<tab>Fé<var 16 /var>li<var 16 /var>ci<var 16 /var>ta<var 16 /var>tions, tu es arrivé<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var><var 1D /var>! Je me demandais qui c'était qui avançait avec autant d'agilité et de maîtrise, mais en te voyant arriver, j'ai tout de suite comprrris<var 1D /var>! Forcément, ce n'est pas ta première par<var 16 /var>ti<var 16 /var>ci<var 16 /var>pa<var 16 /var>tion aux Feux de la Mort<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_POBYANO_000_031<tab>You did it! And just as I thought you would! Don't ask me why, but I had a good feeling about you right from the start! You'd better believe that at least one person who saw you conquer the course today will be strolling into their nearest Adventurers' Guild tomorrow to sign themselves up!
target: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_POBYANO_000_031<tab>Fé<var 16 /var>li<var 16 /var>ci<var 16 /var>ta<var 16 /var>tions, tu es arrivé<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var><var 1D /var>! Je suis sûre que de nombrrreux gens auront eu envie de rejoindre la guilde des aventuriers en te voyant avancer avec tant d'agilité et de maîtrise<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_POBYANO_000_032<tab>I trust you have places to go and people to see, but should you ever wish to show off your skills again for all to see, the Eorzean Nimble Warrior course won't be going anywhere! ...At least, not until the end of the faire. You're welcome to rise to the challenge as many times as you like─simply talk to the chaperone at the starting line if you so desire!
target: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_POBYANO_000_032<tab>Je compte sur toi pour parrrticiper à nouveau<var 1D /var>! Pour ça, tu n'auras qu'à t'adresser à mon collègue qui est au départ<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_POBYANO_000_033<tab>You did it! Once again, you've made our painstakingly constructed course appear about as challenging as a leisurely stroll on the beach! If you'd care to treat the faire-goers to another display of your astounding athletic ability, you're always welcome here!
target: TEXT_FESSUM503_03665_POBYANO_000_033<tab>Fé<var 16 /var>li<var 16 /var>ci<var 16 /var>ta<var 16 /var>tions, tu es arrivé<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var><var 1D /var>! Je dois dire que tu es tellement bon<var 08 E905 ((ne)) (()) /var> que je ne me lasse pas de te voirrr faire le parcours de “Pas dans l'tas”<var 1D /var>! N'hésite pas à participer à nouveau, en tout cas<var 1D /var>!
